{
  "assets": [],
  "blocks": [
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b001",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "进出口权是指企业开展进出口业务的资格， 自2022年12月30日起，国家正式取消外贸经营者备案登记的规定 。拟申请进出口权的企业，需做好以下五步，即可依法自主从事进出口业务。具体办理流程如下，供有意向开展进出口业务企业参阅：",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b002",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "第一步：先办理权限——企业经营范围增项",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b003",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "企业查看营业执照，经营范围中需含“货物进出口”“技术进出口”等表述，若无，请到中山市市场监督管理局办理“经营范围变更”，增加“货物进出口”“技术进出口”经营权限。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b004",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "线上办理：（自行选择）",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b005",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "1.进入广东政务服务网（网址：https://www.gdzwfw.gov.cn/）——企业开办专区——企业变更一件事；",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b006",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "2.中山市市场监督管理局网站——广东政务服务网（全省政务服务一网通办）——企业开办——我要一网通办——企业变更一件事；",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b007",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "3.粤商通App进行办理。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b008",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "线下办理：中山市政务服务中心A区A02-A08企业开办综合窗口（东区博爱六路22号）",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b009",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "咨询电话：0760-89817292",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b010",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "第二步：海关备案——报关单位及相关资质备案",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b011",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "线上办理：进入中国国际贸易单一窗口（网址：https://www.singlewindow.cn/#/）——全部应用——口岸执法申报——企业管理——企业资质——资质备案。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b012",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "注意事项：",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b013",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "1.仅做自理报关单位业务的勾选“进出口货物收发货人”、代理报关单位业务的勾选“报关企业”；",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b014",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "2.申请跨境电商企业的仅勾选“跨境电子商务电商企业”且填写企业网址；",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b015",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "3.统计经济区域应选“中山市其他地区”；",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b016",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "4.英文名称和英文地址需用英文填写不可使用拼音译；",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b017",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "5.英文地址若有“中华人民共和国”应正确填“People’s Republic of China”；",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b018",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "6.备案“出口食品生产企业”的出口国家或地区涉及港澳台的正确填写应是“中国香港、中国澳门、中国台湾”。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b019",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "若报关单位需要获取书面备案登记信息的，可以通过“单一窗口”在线打印《报关单位备案证明》，操作路径：全部应用——口岸执法申报——企业管理——企业资质——资质备案——证书管理——备案证明。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b020",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "线下办理：中山海关驻市政务服务中心A65窗口",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b021",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "咨询电话：0760-89817380",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b022",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "第三步：办理电子口岸卡",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b023",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "电子口岸IC卡（法人卡、操作员卡）新入网企业办理具体流程如下：",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b024",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "线上办理：①登录系统：",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b025",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "企业使用管理员账号登录“中国电子口岸”网站（https://www.chinaport.gov.cn/）——中国电子口岸执法系统——制发卡及数字证书服务系统。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b026",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "②申请办理：",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b027",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "1.点击“提交申请”——办卡申请，进行信息录入并上传附件。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b028",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "2.录入信息：企业基本信息（上传附件）——法人卡信息（上传附件）——操作员卡信息（上传附件）——经办人信息（上传附件）——预览——经办人短信验证——阅读并勾选声明——提交申请。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b029",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "③查询进度：",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b030",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "点击“综合查询”——申请单查询——点击“查看”，根据受理结果取卡。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b031",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "④现场取卡：",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b032",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "经办人需携带申请单位市场主体资格证明材料和本人身份证明材料前往选取的制卡机构领取电子口岸卡。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b033",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "线下办理：中山海关驻市政务服务中心A66窗口",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b034",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "咨询电话：0760-89817391",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b035",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "第四步：办理外汇账户——外汇收支企业名录登记",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b036",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "线上办理：支持银行网银办理",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b037",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "线下办理：境内对公业务商业银行网点",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b038",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "咨询电话：国家外汇管理局中山市分局（0760-88862609）",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b039",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "第五步：办理出口退税备案登记",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b040",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "线上办理：登录电子税务局——我要办税——出口退税管理——出口退（免）税企业资格信息报告——出口退（免）税备案",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b041",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "线下办理：（自行选择）",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b042",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "1.中山市税务局中心片区综合办税服务厅（市政务服务中心）；",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b043",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "2.中山市税务局东部片区综合办税服务厅（开发区）；",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b044",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "3.中山市税务局西部片区综合办税服务厅（小榄）；",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b045",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "4.中山市税务局北部片区综合办税服务厅（黄圃）；",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b046",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "5.中山市税务局南部片区综合办税服务厅（三乡）。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "html_tag": "p"
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_013_zhongshan_import_export_guide_b047",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": null,
      "text": "咨询电话：税务局（12366）",
      "type": "paragraph"
    }
  ],
